{"about_the_game":"West Hunt is an online social deduction game set in the Old West.<br>It's the perfect game to test your detective and stealth skills with your friends in quick, exciting matches.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570330/extras/OUTLAW_BANNER_STEAM.jpg?t=1735042818\" /><br>As an outlaw, you have to complete your missions without being killed by the sheriff.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Bribe the barman.<br></li><li>Poison the water.<br></li><li>Steal from the bank.<br></li><li>Pray and ask for forgiveness.<br></li><li>Tamper with the post board.<br></li><li>Decrease your notoriety by doing side missions.<br></li><li>Much more...</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570330/extras/SHERIFF_BANNER_STEAM.jpg?t=1735042818\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find and kill the outlaw among villagers.<br></li><li>If you shoot a villager you lose.<br></li><li>Investigate and collect information.<br></li><li>Check your mailboxes for more hints. </li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570330/extras/HEADER_KEY_FEATURES.jpg?t=1735042818\" /><br><br><strong>Play mods</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1 VS 1<br></li><li>2 VS 2<br></li><li>3 VS 3<br></li><li>1 VS BOT<br></li><li>CUSTOM</li></ul><br><strong>Everything is Random:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The outlaw missions are randomly generated.<br></li><li>The outlaw skin is also random in each match.<br></li><li>The sheriff gets his mail in random mailboxes as well. </li></ul><br><strong>Stealth</strong>:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The Outlaw can be anyone, a woman an old man, or a native American...<br></li><li>Blending with the villagers and doing side missions to keep low notoriety.</li></ul><br><strong>Communication</strong>:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Both players can use voice chat, thi